ce during use.\",\"As a user, I want the ringer volume to be adjustable, so that I can set it to a comfortable level.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a clear and understandable user interface, so that I can operate it easily.\",\"As a user, I want the ringer to be distinct from other notification sounds, so that I can easily identify an incoming call.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to be easy to clean, so that I can maintain its appearance.\",\"As a user, I want to be able to replace the handset cord if it gets damaged, so that I can continue using the phone without replacing the entire unit.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to be compatible with standard telephone lines, so that it can be easily connected and used.\",\"As a user, I want the dial to have a smooth rotation, so that dialing is effortless.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a comfortable handset grip, so that it is pleasant to hold during long conversations.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a clear audio output for conversations, so that I can hear the other party well.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a clear audio input for my voice, so that the other party can hear me well.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a clear and audible busy signal, so that I know when to try again later.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to be lightweight enough to move easily, so that I can reposition it if needed.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a secure connection for the handset cord, so that it doesn't accidentally disconnect during use.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a clear dial tone, so that I know the phone is connected to the network.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a robust build quality, so that it feels solid and reliable.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a clear and understandable dialing process, so that I can make calls without confusion.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to be available in multiple classic colors, so that I can choose one that matches my style.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a reliable ringer, so that I don't miss important calls.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a clear and distinct busy signal, so that I know the line is occupied.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a comfortable handset rest, so that the handset sits securely when not in use.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a clear and audible disconnect tone, so that I know the call has ended.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a clear and audible ringing sound, so that I don't miss incoming calls.\",\"As a user, I want the phone to have a clear dial tone, so that I know the line is active.\"]}";

